stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Request

    Request --> Retry: Retryable error
    Retry --> Request: Backoff + retry
    Request --> Interrupt: Non-retryable / retries exhausted
    Request --> Response: Model response received

    Response --> Complete: finish_reason=stop AND no tool_calls
    Response --> Yield: followup tool requested
    Response --> Tools: tool_calls present

    Tools --> Append: Execute tools sequentially

    Append --> Interrupt: max tool-failure limit reached
    Append --> Interrupt: max requests/turn reached
    Append --> Request: continue next pass

    Complete --> [*]
    Yield --> [*]
    Interrupt --> [*]

    note right of Request
      on_request hooks run
      (doom-loop detector can inject reminder)
    end note

    note right of Response
      on_response hooks run
      (compaction can mutate context)
    end note
